HUDSON YARDS CATERING  Trademark Information
 UNION SQUARE HOSPITALITY GROUP, LLC
packaged nuts, namely, processed, roasted and shelled nuts; preserved, dried, cooked and processed olives; preserved foods, namely, fruits and vegetables; tapenades; aiolis; oils, namely, olive; dips; snacks, namely, fruit-based, potato-based, vegetable-based, and candied fruit; food spreads, namely, vegetable spread
packaged foods, namely, packaged meals consisting primarily of pasta or rice and packaged entrees consisting primarily of pasta or rice; preserved foods, namely, fruits and vegetables; marinades, salad dressings; condiments, namely, tomato-based and oil-based; sauces, namely, mayonnaise; seasonings, snacks, namely, popped popcorn
non-alcoholic cocktail mixes




