Union Square Hospitality Group, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:37 PM ET
Hotels, Restaurants and Leisure

Company Overview of Union Square Hospitality Group, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Union Square Hospitality Group, LLC owns and operates restaurants and cafes in New York. The company operates fine dining restaurant, a road-side burger restaurant, museum restaurants and cafes, and an off-premise restaurant; and barbecue joints, a jazz club, and a roman trattoria. It also engages in catering and venue hospitality; and consulting and learning businesses. The company was founded in 1985 and is based in New York, New York.


24 Union Square East6th FloorNew York, NY 10003-3201United StatesFounded in 1985



Phone: 212-228-3585

Fax: 212-228-3622

www.ushgnyc.com







