Union Square Hospitality Group LLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























union square hospitality group llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Food Services
Union Square Hospitality Group, LLC provides catering and business services. The Company offers full-scale catering and venue hospitality business, jazz club, and an organizational consulting business services. Union Square Hospitality Group serves customers in the State of New York.




Corporate Information
Address:

24 Union Square East
6th Floor
New York, NY 10003
United States


Phone:
1-212-228-3585


Fax:
-


Web url:
www.ushgnyc.com























