Home /
            



Careers











Careers



























Love Where You Work At Union Square Hospitality Group, our employees come first. Our mission is to nourish individuals, businesses, and communities through the practice of Enlightened Hospitality. This unique approach puts our employees first, because we believe that attracting, hiring, and nurturing the right people is what sets our businesses apart. We aim to find “51%ers”, individuals who embody our Family Values of Excellence, Hospitality, Entrepreneurial Spirit, and Integrity.Each USHG business offers a different path to challenge our employees’ abilities, expand their skills, and reward their contributions, all in an atmosphere that celebrates excellence and growth. We invest in our employees through robust training, mentoring, leadership development programs, and an educational curriculum that touches on every aspect of the hospitality industry, including culinary, service, beverage, and finance courses.With our Hospitality Included initiative, we’ve made a commitment to eliminating tipping at all of our businesses, which allows us to invest in our people through progressive compensation and career advancement support.The Benefits of Working with Us USHG offers competitive compensation, meaningful benefits, and a winning work environment designed around the philosophy of Enlightened Hospitality. We are proud to offer all qualified employees a package of employee benefits including: paid time off; medical, dental and vision insurance; 401(k) with company match; a pre-tax transit program; Flex Spending and Dependent Care Accounts; corporate partner discounts; and an Employee Dining Program.Explore career opportunities with USHG.







Learn More About Careers at USHG








